# Node specs format:
# name|api_key|db_uri|db_type|db_label
#
# Columns:
# - name:      node/organization short name
# - api_key:   node API key (used in generated entities)
# - db_uri:    optional; if empty defaults to DATA_DIR_DEFAULT/<name>.csv
# - db_type:   optional; defaults to csv
# - db_label:  optional; defaults to default

